    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable companion for your daily adventures? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready to hit the road! While it shows some honest signs of its journey so far, it still offers a solid driving experience and plenty of practicality for its next owner. It's a great opportunity to get behind the wheel of a dependable car at a very reasonable price!",
